Usage: print_message [-help] [-id <msg ID> | <formatstring>] [-error] [-warning] [<args <arg1> <arg2> ...>]

-help                        # Prints out the command usage
<formatString>               # Format specifiers like sprintf or Tcl's format
                             # command. (string, optional)
<args <arg1> <arg2> ...>     # The fomat args value to print.
                             # (string, optional)
-error                       # The message is an error. A prefix will be added.
                             # (bool, optional)
-id <string>                 # Specify message id. (string, optional)
-warning                     # The message is an warning. A prefix will be
                             # added. (bool, optional)